Class ParamView

  • java.lang.Object
    • pda.view.ParamView

  • public class ParamView
extends java.lang.Object
    The ParamView is the parameters pages. Access from the PhotoBoostView page.
    It diplays all the parameters changeable on the application
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Florent Catiau-Tristant and Mehdi Haddad
